text: Cesny-les-Sources is a commune. It is found in the region Normandy in the Calvados department in the northwest of France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2019 and consists of the former communes of Acqueville, Angoville, Cesny-Bois-Halbout, Placy and Tournebu.Arrêté préfectoral 24 September 2018, p. 124 == References == Category:2019 establishments in France Category:Communes in Calvados
title: Cesny-les-Sources
